data.title: WTCF 2020 Guidelines Document
data.meta_description: WTCF 2020 Guidelines document - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides guidelines for various cultural competitions at the World Telugu Cultural Festival 2020. It outlines 9 main events including Soundarya Lahari (beauty pageant), Fashion Show, Telugu Velugu (speaking competitions), Andela Ravali (dance), Raaga Manjari (singing), Naadamrutam (instrumental music), Kalaakruti (arts and crafts), Rangasthalam (theatre), and Bhuvana Vijayam (model UN). Specific rules are provided for each sub-event competition, including eligibility, submission requirements, evaluation criteria, and prizes/awards.
